---
import Links from "../components/Links.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
	<div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-6 self-stretch">
		<h1 class="font-400 text-8">Hey 👋🏻, I'm Andrew</h1>
		<p class="self-stretch text-4 lh-[150%]">
			Full Stack Developer by trade and a tech enthusiast at heart, I
			specialize in weaving together the art of design with the
			intricacies of software engineering. My expertise spans from
			creating dynamic web applications with modern frameworks to
			architecting efficient back-end systems, with a strong command over
			Go and Java.
		</p>

		<p class="self-stretch text-4 lh-[150%]">
			Passionate about every facet of product design, I bring a unique
			blend of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and modern frameworks like Astro,
			Svelte, and React to life. My approach is holistic – balancing
			functionality with aesthetics, ensuring every project is not just a
			codebase, but a crafted experience.
		</p>
	</div>

	<Links />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	* {
		margin: 0;
	}
</style>
